data.description: ***BACK ON MARKET! HUGE PRICE REDUCTION***  From the moment you walk up the driveway you will be stunned by the attention to detail throughout this meticulously updated home. A lush landscaped garden surrounds the house. Under the foliage take in the glow of the outdoor fire pit or sip coffee and read the morning paper in your own courtyard! Improve your short game or enjoy some cornhole with its putting green/ cornhole field in complete privacy! Inside, you will immediately notice the upgraded floors, volume ceilings and luxury crown molding all throughout the home. The large open floorplan makes this home superb for entertaining. The kitchen boasts quartz countertops, quiet close cabinets and drawers and a touch activated smart sink. Complete with a custom walk in closet as well as custom shoe closet, the master suite is large enough for an entire king bedroom set. Sliding doors open out to the lanai. The master bath has both a shower and a tiled garden tub as well as dual QUARTZ vanities and separate water closet. The guest suite holds two large bedrooms. Both with their own walk in closets and convenient access to the Jack and Jill bathroom complete with tiled shower. Upstairs, the loft can be easily converted into another bedroom or keep it as a media room with a murphy bed and great view of Lake Griffin. In 2019 the half bath was added off the garage. Making a perfect bathroom for guests or those rainy Florida afternoons! Speaking of rainy days the expanded garage has it's own mud room! The expanded garage has enough room for your vehicles as well as a workshop. Perfectly located, this home is just minutes to all the entertainment and shopping of The Villages.
